title: Senator Qayyum presents his book to prime minister
content:
ISLAMABAD, May 19 (APP): Former Chairman of Senate Standing Committee on Defence Production
Senator Lt General (Retd) Abdul Qayyum on Friday called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here.
The senator presented his book titled “Learning From History” to the prime minister, a PM Office press release said.
